          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>Savvy Stuffies was founded in 2015 by Sarah Johnson, a former emergency room nurse who witnessed firsthand the comfort that stuffed animals brought to children in crisis situations.</p>
          <p>After responding to a house fire where a young girl lost everything, Sarah gave the child her own childhood teddy bear. The transformation in the child's demeanor was immediate and profound.</p>
          <p>This experience inspired Sarah to start collecting stuffed animals to distribute to first responders, hospitals, and shelters. The organization grew from there, eventually adding the innovative "Guns for Toys" program that helps remove unwanted firearms from homes while funding the purchase of new stuffed animals.</p>
        </div>
